{"tid":677793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[港鐵工程]沙中線工程爛透百米隧道大滲漏","createTime":"2018-05-25T13:24:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T04:43:21.000Z","uid":105567,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"087f82b086c43b69f3dcf8521d5e51aeeb2d4f94","tid":677793,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T13:24:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180320/00174_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180320%2F00174_001.html&d=S7eqwRF9ZfCTXic8CoUQf2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=74ca9761\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180320/00174_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n「千億鐵路」港鐵沙中線爆出工程失誤！在紅磡站對出地底趕工興建的鐵路隧道，自去年八月開始出現滲水，工程人員花近半年時間嘗試灌漿及「打針」仍搶救無效，上月漏水情況更惡化。港鐵幾經追查下，發現隧道的接駁工程出問題，結果鑿開其中一個駁口石屎表面調查，赫然發現內部的鋼筋疑未有完全接駁好，而且未有灌滿石屎。工程人員其後再發現多兩處出現相同問題；而隧道上方地面的新建成路軌石屎枕亦有滲水。承建商事後要廿四小時趕工「推倒重來」，除要拆除一百卅多米範圍內三處有同類問題的石屎及重造駁口外，地面更要移除長十米的石屎枕及路軌重鋪。港鐵預計修補工程需時兩個多月，最快下月完成，將向承建商索償。"},{"pid":"f7358b59339783878183a329d0c73652ff766579","tid":677793,"uid":176366,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T13:31:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180320/00174_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180320%2F00174_001.html&d=S7eqwRF9ZfCTXic8CoUQf2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=74ca9761\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180320/00174_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n「千億鐵路」港鐵沙中線爆出工程失誤！在紅磡站對出地底趕工興建的鐵路隧道，自去年八月開始出現滲水，工程人員花近半年時間嘗試灌漿及「打針」仍搶救無效，上月漏水情況更惡化。港鐵幾經追查下，發現隧道的接駁工程出問題，結果鑿開其中一個駁口石屎表面調查，赫然發現內部的鋼筋疑未有完全接駁好，而且未有灌滿石屎。工程人員其後再發現多兩處出現相同問題；而隧道上方地面的新建成路軌石屎枕亦有滲水。承建商事後要廿四小時趕工「推倒重來」，除要拆除一百卅多米範圍內三處有同類問題的石屎及重造駁口外，地面更要移除長十米的石屎枕及路軌重鋪。港鐵預計修補工程需時兩個多月，最快下月完成，將向<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">市民</span></span></strong>索償。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7a72095ef0afe3d26a8e1bee5ae6e66679c63458","tid":677793,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T13:35:30.000Z","msg":"立會又要撥多一百億了<br />\nFatfat"},{"pid":"f6caa71dbb3a9585176221f1caca1d0d6b9c10e4","tid":677793,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T13:36:35.000Z","msg":"gdp sink<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf837b850bc07ed18db0e2fe7adb7fe447626c6","tid":677793,"uid":113178,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f6caa71dbb3a9585176221f1caca1d0d6b9c10e4","tid":677793,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T13:36:35.000Z","msg":"gdp sink<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T13:53:06.000Z","msg":"無限GDP <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78535ed1da7271c785591b09238658f22a396d68","tid":677793,"uid":135767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T14:01:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa239f67a7df5c4f5b213669ab2a8fb6077433fb","tid":677793,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T14:07:38.000Z","msg":"最近因報經常爆港鐵<br />\n有人得罪左佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d782043bffcdfc8786fbbf35046cf66a7765230d","tid":677793,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T14:16:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"027b5851b55b470a74c3470f748dfaa07bccdec2","tid":677793,"uid":20816,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T14:21:14.000Z","msg":"東方越多仇口，得益嘅係市民"},{"pid":"1f3afd94bc03da85d16259b342b0938cd9700d33","tid":677793,"uid":60665,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d782043bffcdfc8786fbbf35046cf66a7765230d","tid":677793,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T14:16:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T17:24:00.000Z","msg":"嗰時港鐵怕左因報即時炒左個實Q<br />\n結果都係逃唔過俾因報追擊既命運<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a59b94ecde729cfe1573f4ec94c24c741eaf126","tid":677793,"uid":116443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T19:24:37.000Z","msg":"2018年3月20日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f9f3ec23f737534c172c95b4bef746d22523b85","tid":677793,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T22:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc3e0e66c5d77eb43424d1c5c611866fea6c7a13","tid":677793,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:43:21.000Z","msg":"大白象一定要爛先得黎大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}